{"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme\/init(borders:colors:colorModes:charts:elevations:fonts:grids:opacities:dimensions:sizes:spaces:badge:bulletList:button:checkbox:chip:controlItem:divider:icon:link:pinCodeInput:quantityInput:radioButton:selectInput:skeleton:switch:tag:inputTag:textArea:textInput:resourcesBundle:name:family:tuning:)"],"title":"Initializers","generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme is the bsic, default, theme for any Orange products."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is an override of the abtract "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"must be seen as the default theme for the OUDSThemesContract library","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It can override any properties from its superclass, and can be derived too."}],"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme"],"title":"Inherits From","kind":"relationships","type":"inheritsFrom"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s16SendableMetatypeP"],"title":"Conforms To","kind":"relationships","type":"conformsTo"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeBrandColorRawTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeBrandFontRawTokens"],"title":"Group","generated":true,"anchor":"Group"}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Class","symbolKind":"class","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeTheme"}],"role":"symbol","title":"OrangeTheme","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B5ThemeC","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}]},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":1,"anchor":"Usages","text":"Usages","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Any Orange products must use this theme. It provides core and Orange colors and any elements for sizings, spacings and dimensions for example.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The system font families are used; no ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helevetica"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" font family is embeded nor provider by OUDSThemesContract.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This theme also provides colors charts tokens.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The theme can be got through environment variable:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    @Environment(\\.theme) var theme"],"type":"codeListing"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Integration","text":"Integration","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To use this theme, inject it to your view using ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSThemeableView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and get it through environment variable.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    @main","    struct YourApp: App {","        var body: some Scene {","            WindowGroup {","                OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeTheme()) {","                    \/\/ Your root view","                }","            }","        }","    }"],"type":"codeListing"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Theme-tuning","text":"Theme tuning","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The theme can be customized a bit for more flexibility thanks to "},{"code":"Tuning","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" object."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You just need to give a predefined tuning configuration at theme init to build the one you need."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To apply the tuning:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Define your theme tuning","    let tuning = Tuning(hasRoundedButtons: true, hasRoundedTextInputs: true)","","    \/\/ Apply it to your theme","    let theme = OrangeTheme(tuning: tuning)","    \/\/ Or in one line","    let theme = OrangeTheme(tuning: Tuning(hasRoundedButtons: true, hasRoundedTextInputs: true))","","    \/\/ Or apply predefined tunings","    let orangeFranceTheme = OrangeTheme(tuning: Tuning.OrangeFrance)","    let orangeBusinessTheme = OrangeTheme(tuning: Tuning.OrangeBusiness)","    let maxitTheme = OrangeTheme(tuning: Tuning.MaxIt)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Typography","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Typography"},{"anchor":"Helvetica-Neue","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Helvetica Neue"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange brand strongly relies on the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helvetica Neue"}]},{"type":"text","text":" font family. Thus each Orange brand should, or must, use it."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For iOS the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helvetica Neue"}]},{"type":"text","text":" font family is available at system level, so it is not needed to get it through external assets."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"By default an instance of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" uses as font family the token "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeBrandFontRawTokens.familyBrandDefault"},{"type":"text","text":", which is today "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helvetica Neue"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you want to use another font family, you will have to send the suitable token or the suitable font family."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, beware, iOS API relies also on the PostScript name of the font."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"To be sure of the value to use, look at the font book of your device."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is recommended to use the font raw tokens."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ The following instanciations work","    let orangeTheme = OrangeTheme()","    let orangeTheme = OrangeTheme(family: OrangeBrandFontRawTokens.familyBrandDefault)","    let orangeTheme = OrangeTheme(family: \"HelveticaNeue\") \/\/ Which is PostScript name of the font","    let orangeTheme = OrangeTheme(family: \"Helvetica Neue\") \/\/ Which is font family nale"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","text":"Helvetica Neue Arabic","anchor":"Helvetica-Neue-Arabic","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Because the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Helvetica Neue","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" font family does not manage arabic alphabet but latin one, it is possible apply another font family to the theme like the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helvetica Neue Arabic"}]},{"type":"text","text":". This font family assets can be retrieved through the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/brand.orange.com\/en\/brand-basics\/typography","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"PostScript name management has been implemented for this font family, thus the weight are managed and it is only needed to add the font assets to the project,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"register them and define the font family name to use."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    let orangeTheme = OrangeTheme(family: \"Helvetica Neue Arabic\")"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","text":"Tokens loading","anchor":"Tokens-loading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can also use some tokens providers defined in your side, but they must match the same type as the one used on the themes (see "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":")."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For example:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["   \/\/ Use some already defined providers","   let borders = OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider()","   let sizes = OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider()","   let spaces = OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider()","","   \/\/ For example, use your own provider of color semantic tokens","   \/\/ It must inherit from OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider (which is instance of AllColorSemanticTokensProvider) or directly implement AllColorSemanticTokensProvider","   let colors = YourOwnColorSemanticTokensProvider()","","   \/\/ Some providers need other providers to use their tokens","   let button = OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider(sizes: sizes, borders: borders, colors: colors, spaces: spaces)","","   \/\/ But you can also use the providers as they are without assigning semantic tokens providers","   \/\/ and just use the default ones","   let badge = OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider()","","   \/\/ Define in the end your theme by overriding some providers.","   \/\/ You can override all providers, or only some, or just keep the theme as is.","   \/\/ However you should uses thhese providers in a dedicated Orange theme subclass for clarity reasons.","   let yourOwnOrangeTheme = OrangeTheme(colors: colors, borders: borders, sizes: sizes, spaces: spaces, button: button, badge: badge)"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.8.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note","name":"Since"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangetheme"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"https://brand.orange.com/en/brand-basics/typography":{"title":"Orange Brand website (authentication needed)","identifier":"https:\/\/brand.orange.com\/en\/brand-basics\/typography","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"Orange Brand website (authentication needed)","type":"text"}],"type":"link","url":"https:\/\/brand.orange.com\/en\/brand-basics\/typography"},"ic_theme_orange.png":{"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"image","alt":null,"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeTheme":{"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","title":"OrangeTheme","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme is the bsic, default, theme for any Orange products."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This is an override of the abtract ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"must be seen as the default theme for the OUDSThemesContract library","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It can override any properties from its superclass, and can be derived too.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangetheme","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme","kind":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeBrandColorRawTokens":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeBrandColorRawTo